<A>__{korda has one eye on the road and the other on the rear view mirror. the cadillac is making up ground.}
<B>__{up ahead}
<A>__{a squad car screeches into the intersection and smokes to a stop. korda jerks the wheel, pulls a screaming right turn and heads up the hill.}
<L>__{exterior street day}
<A>__{the cadillac is only about a hundred feet behind the van... brakes squealing, it swerves around the corner in pursuit.}
<B>__{the van}
<A>__{hits the top of the hill and goes airborne... slams back down to the pavement.}
